@optional {Qualifier: str}

@endgroup

@group 2018-10-31
@endpoint DELETE /2018-10-31/layers/{LayerName}/versions/{VersionNumber}
@desc Deletes a version of an Lambda layer. Deleted versions can no longer be viewed or added to functions. To avoid breaking functions, a copy of the version remains in Lambda until no functions refer to it.
@required {LayerName: str, VersionNumber: int(i64)}

@endgroup

